# Sovrunn Testing Rules

Every Phase 1 feature must include tests.

Minimum expected tests:

- resource validation happy path
- resource validation failure path
- registry create/get/list/update/delete
- duplicate name tests
- missing reference tests where applicable
- delete-blocked tests where applicable
- API handler happy path
- API handler error path

Feature is not complete until tests pass.
